## Create product (manga_volume) — admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "id_franchise": 2,
    "product_type": "manga_volume",
    "name": "The Apothecary Diaries Vol. 1",
    "price": 10.99,
    "stock": 20,
    "sku": "MNG-APD-001",
    "details": {
        "id_publisher": 3,
        "id_media": 4,
        "volume": 1
    }
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":201,"msg":"Product created successfully","data":{"id":12},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 02:50:51"}
